data.enText: used to introduce more exact and detailed information about sth that you have just mentioned

data.chText: 我们须针对我们的听众对象，即年龄在20到30岁之间的妇女。
data.enText: We need to concentrate on our target audience, namely women aged between 20 and 30.

value.def: You use namely to introduce detailed information about the subject you are discussing, or a particular aspect of it.

example.ex: One group of people seems to be forgotten, namely pensioners...
example.tran: 有一类人似乎被遗忘了，就是那些领养老金的人。

example.ex: They were hardly aware of the challenge facing them, namely, to re-establish prosperity.
example.tran: 他们几乎没有意识到自己面临的挑战，即再创繁荣。
